### 2. API Key Setup & Security

1. Log in to your [Stripe Dashboard](https://dashboard.stripe.com/).
2. Navigate to **Developers > API keys** to get your Publishable and Secret keys.
3. For the Webhook secret, run the Stripe CLI (see Testing section) or configure a webhook endpoint in the dashboard.
4. Create a Subscription Product in Stripe and copy the **Price ID** (e.g., `price_1N...`).

**`.env.example`** (Backend root)
```env
